snippet: The outcome was never in question as Duke cruised past Temple and improved to 9-0 for the 15th time under Coach Mike Krzyzewski.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Duke defeats Temple, 90-67, to reach 9-0 for 15th time under coach Mike Krzyzewski; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The outcome was never in question as Duke cruised past Temple and improved to 9-0 for the 15th time under Coach Mike Krzyzewski.

headline.seo: Duke Shows Coach Krzyzewski a Virtue He Values in Win Over Temple
headline.main: Duke Shows Krzyzewski a Quality He Values
headline.print_headline: Defeating Temple, No. 2 Duke Reaches 9-0 for 15th Time Under Krzyzewski
